# Core Rules (TCSgon)

Strict TypeScript (strict + noUncheckedIndexedAccess + exactOptionalPropertyTypes).
No `any`. No `@ts-ignore` without ticket. No class components. No `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` without justification.
State order: local → Context → React Query → Redux Toolkit.
Accessibility WCAG 2.2 AA. Performance budgets enforced.
Tests required: behavior, not implementation.
No secrets in source. CSP enforced.
See `AGENTS.md` for the full ruleset.